Surface height

Source: R/surface.R
surface.Rd

Surface height of central Argentina on a lambert grid.

Usage

surface

Format

A data.table with 53224 rows and 5 variables.

lon

longitude in degrees

lat

latitude in degrees

height

height in meters

x

x coordinates of projection

y

y coordinates of projection
